ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:20:59.000Z","msg":"而家啲考自動波確實你唔入N波 聽講係話Prius 果款車係N波嘅時候叉唔到電 好容易整壞部車。另外你話考線嘅問題 考牌官三條線都有機會考 唔好話駁佢係後備線 而覺得佢唔考。<br />\n<br />\n利申:朋友屋企人係教車師傅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:23:16.000Z","msg":"補多句 自己揸車 知道燈口等候時間較長 都會入手掣空波"},{"pid":"97415368ceb7998367b61f75a2f444ccec7fe72a","tid":530574,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"考過培正<br />\n<br />\n三條線機率都差唔多架咋<br />\n<br />\n自動波停燈位, 如果你想鬆迫力就入N波,手制<br />\n<br />\n但係係可以照用D波, 一定要踩住迫力同拉手制,  總之你唔入N波就唔可以鬆迫力"},{"pid":"dc0ef604af4d2801cda66d3e45a8ef535968cf84","tid":530574,"uid":65367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6318308ddb836433e6401ea01628f7350552e8","tid":530574,"uid":41345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"下星期一考lm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"我都係下星期一考，巴打幾點"},{"pid":"412e1a9bdae7867c0adf3bacf665f15d57dac697","tid":530574,"uid":35307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"入個N波要幾多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都做唔切係你太慢"},{"pid":"606aecf4c5771bc0da61ad6361a9441af8f361f3","tid":530574,"uid":139440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"前排考培正道一次pass比小小意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我考路線2，考果陣係繁忙時間多車，有啲位又塞緊車，可能係咁所以行最短依條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最唔熟果條因爲練得兩三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個過程最緊要安全，望鏡另頭望盲區要做足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於N波，我師傅無講過停燈位要轉N波，我停燈位只係踩迫力同拉手制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005a923a37ca9a67bd5e7a365dfb34e62460b130","tid":530574,"uid":41345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0ef604af4d2801cda66d3e45a8ef535968cf8